{
  "texts": [
    "3 Moreover, the newly introduced EU AI Act (AIA) also calls for safer, transparent, traceable, non-discriminatory, and sustainable AI systems.",
    "In addition to the research gap in scholarly contribution, these policy requirements advocate the need to investigate explainable recommendation systems from the perspective of end users.",
    "Therefore, to address the research gaps mentioned above and to contribute to the literature discussed previously, we undertake this study and address the following research questions: RQ1.",
    "Why do users require explanations for AI-based content suggestions/recommendations in social media?",
    "How do users want the explanations to be presented/ delivered, and how will access to explanations impact their usage?"
  ]
}